{"type": "article", "id": 28139, "title": "如果你在纽约碰到这辆车，别忘了买一支冰激凌", "description": "又是一个街头餐饮的好案例。", "date": "2016-06-13T17:37:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 7518, "name": "冰激凌"}, {"id": 117, "name": "纽约"}, {"id": 140, "name": "街头"}, {"id": 28912, "name": "Van Leeuwen"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 13, "praise_count": 255, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607031205452RIaDGeJykf1ZOnx.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>纽约曼哈顿的 26 号码头，一辆鹅黄色冰激凌车前已排起了长长的队，人们拿着样式非常可爱的甜筒冰激凌走在路上，一脸幸福和满足。他们也许是提前在 Twitter 上看到了每日更新的地址，也许仅仅是路过，但这道街景就足以让人们停下来看一看，顺便也带走一支冰激凌。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120540urY9CMPqdSbtKNOH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66615385\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120540i7cPWyt4oaCfYLks.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5483871\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120540PMjuEs7R0ZYwUQmv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49915683\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>这辆流动餐车属于甜品品牌  <a href=\"http://www.vanleeuwenicecream.com/zgeq74tipq31ht06gyfmow28twggjt\">Van Leeuwen Artisan Ice Cream</a>，由三位年轻人于 2008 年创立，他们在纽约和洛杉矶两地都有这种流动车，每天更新地址，换不同的地方停下来卖冰激凌。在寸土寸金的大都市，这是不算少见但也极为聪明的做法。</p>\n<p>“我们得到了纽约这个惊人的地理位置而没有付任何租金，” Ben Van Leeuwen说道，“这就像一场梦。”</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120541auVgw0P59NtJWYSK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>这家冰激凌的好口碑还在于它的卖相和用料。经典系列使用了据说不添加激素和抗生素的鲜牛奶、奶油、蔗糖和蛋黄，它还有十几种口味选择，能增加干果等配料，可爱的造型让你忘记这是一支售价 7 美元的冰激凌。创立者希望回归到传统冰激凌的售卖和制作方式，在品牌成立几周后，《<a href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2008/07/09/dining/09unde.html?_r=0\">纽约时报</a>》就报道称“提高了街头食物的标准”。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120541zUkR63gEstIyc5Tw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.34074074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120542pCoOJnTXYqezZFuw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>冰激凌品牌发展得非常快，美国大众型的服饰品牌 Old Navy 就曾与他们合作营销，将餐车刷成特别的蓝色，在纽约市免费发放冰激凌。这样做想必是看中街头冰激凌的传播力。</p>\n<p>现在 Van Leeuwen 在纽约和洛杉矶两地有 8 家甜品店，周五、周六的时候都会卖到半夜。他们还出版了一本书记录品牌成立的故事和菜谱的书在<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Van-Leeuwen-Artisan-Ice-Cream/dp/0062329588/175-9469010-0694423?ie=UTF8&amp;keywords=van%20leeuwen&amp;qid=1434476679&amp;ref_=sr_1_1&amp;sr=8-1\">亚马逊</a>上出售，冰激凌清凉香甜的口感仿佛从书和图片的另一头就传了过来。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120542CvEO5gtYVZPfN734.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.48\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Old Navy × Van Leeuwen</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120543EYSnGxDly7C0t43J.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.99667221\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120543brAG521NS6gRVLiX.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120544jeA2z7U4Xdt5vEfp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49866667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120544wq2AVi7KflnC1JPF.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>          </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Van Leeuwen Artisan Ice Cream</p></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.everydayobject.us/2016/06/07/van-leeuwen/\">everydayobject</a>、<a href=\"http://www.vanleeuwenicecream.com/zgeq74tipq31ht06gyfmow28twggjt\">Van Leeuwen Artisan Ice Cream</a></p>\n\n"}